  "slug": "vegetarian-wellington",
  "title": "Vegetarian Wellington",
  "subtitle": "Mushroom, chestnut, and walnut filling wrapped in puff pastry, a show-stopping centrepiece",
  "excerpt": "A vegetarian wellington is a firm, flavourful log of mushroom duxelles, chestnuts, walnuts, and cream cheese wrapped in puff pastry and baked until deeply golden. The key is drying the filling completely before wrapping: any moisture will make the pastry soggy from inside.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "Contemporary British vegetarian cooking. Adapted from the beef Wellington tradition (19th century). Yotam Ottolenghi and the broader vegetarian centrepiece cooking tradition in British food from the 2010s onwards.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The central challenge of a vegetarian ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "wellington filling",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpdr5od30000f4v4n3gohybj"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " is moisture. Mushrooms and spinach both contain large amounts of water that must be cooked out before they are combined with the other ingredients. If they go into the pastry wet, the moisture escapes during baking and the base turns soft.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The filling must be cold before the pastry goes on. Warm filling makes the pastry greasy and prevents the sharp base crust forming. Refrigerate it for at least 30 minutes after the ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "pastry is sealed",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpdr5oe20001f4v4ez7hzjcx"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " around it.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What you need",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
